This function block contains all logic for controlling a Sabload module. -This module consists of a jig, table, airbag part detection layser sensors.
>> Block created by: Engr. Awais Ali >> Block creation date: 08-10-2025
if the 1st part place on the Jig for x seconds the state move from 0 to 5. It confirm the part is there.
